# 🌍 ClimatePulse AI

## 🧠 Overview
ClimatePulse AI is a machine learning project that analyzes climate data and estimates its impact on productivity and risk levels.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Climate data analysis
- Machine learning model
- Productivity prediction
- Risk classification system

---

## 🎯 Goal
Transform climate data into actionable insights for decision making.

---

## 👨‍💻 Status
Prototype project (Academic use)